title: Cuffed To The Crowd // Cuffing Season (Part 8) //Jimmy Rollins
description: In between your crisis and your creator is your crowd. Will you let the crowd cripple your calling? Or will you push through the crowd, walk in your calling, and make contact with your creator. In week 8 of Cuffing Season, special guest Jimmy Rollins brings a powerful message teaching us the ways to ignore the crowd to get to our calling. If this message is encouraging to you, let us know & share it with a friend!
